    {
      "id": "1924750c-f3ba-80de-89c8-ee0fd2c84d47",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "DKT is a state-of-the-art technique that predicts a learner’s performance based on observed learning history. However, learning history does not account for the whole picture: guessing, partial understanding, etc… To include a measurement of these elemente, the authors propose Variational Deep Knowledge Tracing (VDKT), which uses latent variables to incorporate their stochasticity.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "1924750c-f3ba-80de-89c8-ee0fd2c84d47",
